:

1. *Sine* su se igrali ispred kuće. (The children were playing in front of the house).
2. Ona je imala *sinove* i kćerke. (She had sons and daughters).
3. On se poigravao sa *sinom* svog prijatelja. (He was playing with his friend's son).
4. *Sinovi* su poslušali majku. (The sons listened to their mother).
5. Ona je pokazala svoje *sine* fotografiju. (She showed her son a photograph).